* `0`: run at exactly 0 seconds of each minute
* `0/15`: run every 15 minutes
* `0-23`: run every hour from 00:00 to 23:00
* `*`: run every day of the month
* `*`: run every month
* `*`: run every day of the week

You can adjust the cron expression according to your specific needs. Also, make sure to set the correct timezone in your application configuration to ensure that the scheduled task runs at the desired local time.

